Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[intense music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to announce\Nmy engagement to Light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Pop Music Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to really like Kira too,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know for sure\Nthat Light is gonna catch him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[bangs the table, glass clatters]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for you,\Nyou'll probably be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're to send me a fan letter\Nthat I'll be able to recognize as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You will also enclose something else\Nin the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Five blank pages from the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry on with your judgements and killings\Nas usual
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,until I receive the letter and the pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] And how about\Nafter you receive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] Make a notebook that looks\Nas close to the original as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and act as if you're killing people\Nby using this decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] Oh, come on now, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, wearing a short skirt like that\Nin the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's getting off the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,VIGILANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who was on the same train\Nas Mikami just collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He was harassing a young woman\Nand suddenly fell to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It all happened about half a minute\Nafter he wrote something in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s gotta be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now we know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,X-KIRA\NMIKAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Our next order of business\Nis to get as close as possible to Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But before we rush in blindly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something\Nwe need to be careful of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And that…\Nis the being known as the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shinigami will be loyal to Mikami
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and will warn him if he discovers\Nwe're following him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Shinigami can only be seen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,by those people\Nwho have touched the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be pretty difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to be careful of something\Nwe can't even see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] We're gonna try,\Nno matter how difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[static noise]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Light is having another one\Nof his meetings with Takada this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after they started having\Nthese encounters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Takada got a phone call from Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the surveillance cameras\Nhad to be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing that came to my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,was that they'd be able\Nto communicate secretly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,by writing messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Everything checks out in here.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone over the entire room\Nand there's nothing in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only the wiretap on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Uh… right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all that's left is the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does Light care so much\Nabout checking for cameras and wiretaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Kira allowing these meetings\Nin the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Something just doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If they really are\Nwriting notes to each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,there's only one way to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, I thought you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a private chat\Nwith Miss Misa Amane yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Oh, boy! Light's in trouble now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda, is there some reason\Nyou're so happy about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me that she's planning\Nto announce her engagement to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,during her appearance\Nat the Pop Music Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT IS MISA TO YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he is busted. Light's in the doghouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No. She thinks we're together
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because I haven't been able\Nto break it to her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But she means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why pull a stunt like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Takada. You're just as bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are women like this? [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:04:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light's voice] She was\Nin charge of killing before T.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, she gained\Nthe same power as I had
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and found out that I was Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I had no choice\Nbut to take her as my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only reason I would ever choose\Nsuch an impulsive girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] So, Misa was doing\NKira's killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now,\NI'm the one doing it for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Light had no choice with Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But he chose me specially to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me, she's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're the only one for me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to be serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected better from you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] She does have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's a pretty cheesy line for Light.\N-[Light] Sorry. That's just how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ide] Do you think he will pick\NAmane or Takada?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] I wonder\Nhow many women you've said that to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] He could keep two-timing them.\N-[Light] You think I'm that kind of guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ide] You don't see a problem with that?\N-[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] Hey, I'm not the one--\N-Will you two shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have to\Nprove yourself from now on, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, if I find out\Nthat you're lying, you'll pay dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'll tell Kira about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I understand that the world\Nreally needs Kira right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just can't help but wonder,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,will the day ever come\Nwhen you and I can be together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but hate Kira\Nfor choosing you as his spokesperson
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because it keeps us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if he kills criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but we've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the right\Nto lead happy lives, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yes, I want\Nto be happy together with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"But that could only happen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,if Kira wasn't around."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If only Kira wasn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,should be arrested."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you and I are ever going\Nto have a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of being happy together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira needs to be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you seriously mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I'm going to arrest him,\NI'll need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be putting yourself in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] After all,\NI'll be defying the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll be going against Kira\Nand the entire world as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a long pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"If cooperating with you\Nmeans that we can be together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm prepared\Nto make that sacrifice, Light."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What a turnaround!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you'd expect from our guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was able to move the conversation\Nfrom cheating on Misa-Misa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to getting Takki to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikami is talking to himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] He's too far away from me\Nto pick up his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I recorded video of his lips moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sending you the footage\NI was able to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's of Mikami during his lunchbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it right here.\NHe's saying something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] Show it to us one more time\Nin slow motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Is that you, Shinigami?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] He seems to have reacted\Nto the scrap of paper at his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] He just gave a small sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] At this point\Nhe talks to himself a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna zoom in on his lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] That Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,since
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,he…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,handed me the notebook…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,he hasn't reappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"That Shinigami. Ever since\Nhe handed me the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,he hasn't reappeared."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Mikami was given the notebook\Nby one of the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems that\NShinigami hasn't been following him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] [grunting] It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, things got pretty intense today,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough to do this for hours on end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you really look\Nlike you're suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] All right. I'm gonna\Nwrap things up at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I feel kind of bad\Nthat Aizawa is stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with booking the hotel\Nand checking out every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The mark I left is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I left four marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of them are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The room's been left just as it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Housekeeping hasn't come in yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how and why would anyone\Nswitch these two notepads for new ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're writing notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone ringing]\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to meet\Nand talk with Near in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Aizawa, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very nice of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but kinda hard to accept\Nwhile I'm blindfolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have\Nany weapons or cameras on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,\Nyou're free to take off your blindfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Near,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe what you said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,L has been meeting Takada\Nalmost every single night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Near] I know.\N-Wha…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They are passing notes to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Mr. Aizawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't take any unnecessary actions\Non your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Unnecessary actions?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes. This is not the point
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,where we bring up evidence against Kira\Nand openly confront him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I must corner him in a dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with a plan that\Nwould guarantee his defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it will take\Nto stop him for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Aizawa,\NI'm going to be blunt with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You and the rest of the task force\Nare already out of the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] However, if you still want\Nto help capture Kira, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want you to do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is keep an eye on him\Nas you've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it? Keep an eye on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,there certainly is a purpose\Nin watching over L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I've already\Ntaken it into account
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as a part of my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm hoping\Nyou can help me in that respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to win against Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be a witness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to the end of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,NHN HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] This has been a year\Nof breakthroughs for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm sure for many others as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And what better way to bring this year\Nto an exciting close
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,than with the East West\NPop Music Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your host for this evening,\NKiyomi Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We hope you all enjoy the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] All right.\NThe Pop Music Festival is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ide] Matsuda, shouldn't you be\Nchecking over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the reports on Kira's killings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in a minute.\NBut after Misa-Misa performs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the opening act this year.\NWe gotta cheer her on. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] C-- Can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-[door opens]\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me. We're from the SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need you to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we continue,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I must apologize\Non behalf of the staff of NHN.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very unfortunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems that this year's opening act\NMiss Misa Amane
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,has not entered the concert hall yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] Of course…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-many unexpected things can…\N-[Aizawa] What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mogi didn't tell us anything about this.\N-It's always full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Take me back to NHN right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to ruin my reputation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa-Misa, you've got to try\Nand stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mochi, why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] We need to do this\Nin order to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] But that has nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know that I was going\Nto take you at gunpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,as a last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a great help.\NThank you, Mr. Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] I probably would have resisted
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,if I hadn't listened\Nto what Aizawa told me. But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,after hearing about the notepads,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,there’s no doubt in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm… What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes, what is it, L?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] We have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi and Misa Amane have gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I'm already aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who took them into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! He what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Near,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,kidnapping is a blatant criminal act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Actually, Mr. Mogi and Amane\Nboth came here willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can even ask them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put them on the line now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mogi, Misa, this is L speaking.\N-[Misa] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'm told\Nthat Near is detaining you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that you both agreed to it.\NIs that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Mogi…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was against the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mochi said it would be best\Nif I just went along quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me we would have both\Nbeen killed if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine as long as you both\Nconsented to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now I've removed Misa Amane,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who might be the Second Kira,\Nfrom the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the significance of this move\Nisn't lost on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] No way! You're planning to end this\Nwithout Misa-Misa performing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,God, what a rip-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] It looks like Lidner\Nand the others were successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-[woman] Yeah!\N-[man] We want our money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] It's past nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikami leaves work\Nat almost the same time every day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with only slight variations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He leads a completely scheduled life\Nfor the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he always goes\Nto that particular gym
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,every Monday and Thursday\Nat around nine o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's kept that routine\Nfor the past four years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since he joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't even skip New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a member\Nand made a few inquiries
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to confirm it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. So, then can we assume
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that he'll be there\Non Monday the 31st as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] Yes. If he's the type of man\Nwho would go on holidays,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then he'll certainly\Ngo on New Year’s Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Gevanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible for you\Nto touch the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,on the 31st at the gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already done a thorough check\Nof the hotel security.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The locker room is definitely free\Nof any kind of surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Then I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, if there is a Shinigami with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a distinct possibility\Nthat I will die, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of the reason you're doing this\Nis to test that theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't see any Shinigami\Nafter first touching the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to continue\Nwatching Mikami for a while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,before we conclude whether or not\Nhe has one following him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can have Rester do it\Nif you're too scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[heart beating loudly]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni]\NIf there's a Shinigami around--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, if there was one, I'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[heartbeat getting louder]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I've succeeded\Nin touching the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't confirm the existence\Nof any Shinigami
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Commander Rester,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,please connect me with Mr. Mogi\Nfor a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,According to your investigation\Non the rules of the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,how long can a person\Nbe controlled before their death?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the data\Nwe got from Yotsuba's experiments,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it's 23 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say that the killings done by Yotsuba\Nwere more than enough to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Thank you for your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to consider the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that Gevanni is already being controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, they could be making him\Nsay that there is no Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I need to confront L\Nin exactly 24 days…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if Gevanni is still alive until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,JANUARY 3
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Kiyomi, I saw you had some trouble\Nat the Pop Music Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I never imagined\Nthat Miss Amane would go missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light's voice]\N"Give T an order to contact you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and let you know as soon\Nas he's confirmed everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Once you hear from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to send me a text message\Nor call me with the following message,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,'I want to see you as soon as possible'".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,JANUARY 6
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] Photographs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see exactly\Nwhat he wrote in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see the pattern\Nin how Mikami writes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,if there are any habits,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and what kind of notebook it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything in detail,\Nwith my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[camera shutter clicking]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[mysterious music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] What do you think, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Perfect.\NGevanni has done an excellent job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The handwriting matches that\Nof the records Mikami keeps as prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's absolutely no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, we can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
